snippet.textDisplay:
Let me share something interesting.


The original singer Ms. Krishna Patel was our neighbour in All India Radio colony because my father was the senior announcer there and her brother was the station engineer. The original composer Late Mr. Prabhudatta Pradhan was also there in the same colony with his family and he was my music teacher. I have learnt music from him. My childhood was surrounded by these music lover personalities. Have grown up watching them making amazing music in AIR studio, Sambalpur. My father is now retired since 2012. But I still miss Prabhudutta sir inviting us for Christmas 🎄 holidays to have snacks and rose cake with them. Auntie used to make amazing rose cakes. 

Golden Childhood. 😍
snippet.textOriginal:
